558
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:22,400
But I've retired already.

559
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,520
In my dreams,

560
00:37:25,560 --> 00:37:28,480
I still see myself
defeating my fencing opponents.

561
00:37:28,840 --> 00:37:30,840
However, every time I wake up,

562
00:37:31,080 --> 00:37:32,440
I'm clear that

563
00:37:32,560 --> 00:37:33,920
it was just a dream.

564
00:37:36,640 --> 00:37:37,480
You're right.

565
00:37:38,480 --> 00:37:39,520
Something,...

566
00:37:40,000 --> 00:37:40,880
somebody...

567
00:37:41,640 --> 00:37:44,400
should be let go when the time comes.

568
00:37:45,840 --> 00:37:47,600
After getting my postgraduate degree,...

569
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:49,640
I'll continue hosting kids' shows.

570
00:37:50,440 --> 00:37:51,360
That's nice.

571
00:37:51,400 --> 00:37:53,080
Gorgeous and glamorous.

572
00:37:55,160 --> 00:37:58,080
I just love hosting kids' shows,

573
00:37:58,120 --> 00:37:59,920
the way I love rhythmic gymnastics.

574
00:38:00,120 --> 00:38:01,720
It's a heartfelt feeling.

575
00:38:01,920 --> 00:38:03,440
It's not what people say

576
00:38:03,480 --> 00:38:05,720
for the glamor of appearing on TV.

577
00:38:07,000 --> 00:38:09,840
Alright. You're right on everything.

578
00:38:10,240 --> 00:38:11,280
If I've got the chance,...

579
00:38:11,680 --> 00:38:13,360
I'd like to open an art space...

580
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:15,480
for old friends and old teammates

581
00:38:15,520 --> 00:38:16,840
to get together.

582
00:38:17,360 --> 00:38:19,040
It's actually a good idea.

583
00:38:19,240 --> 00:38:20,760
It's trendy to do this now.

584
00:38:20,800 --> 00:38:22,080
It'll get so popular.

585
00:38:23,000 --> 00:38:24,080
Cut it out.

586
00:38:24,120 --> 00:38:26,080
I'm not doing this to get popular.

587
00:38:26,120 --> 00:38:28,360
Okay, I believe you.

588
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:31,880
How about you, Jiang Ze?

589
00:38:32,280 --> 00:38:34,160
What's your plan for the future?

590
00:38:36,400 --> 00:38:37,480
Me.

591
00:38:37,520 --> 00:38:40,400
I've just applied for a job
in Shenghai Group.

592
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:44,160
I still don't know if Shenghai Group
would hire me or not.

593
00:38:44,840 --> 00:38:46,240
They'll surely do.

594
00:38:46,280 --> 00:38:47,680
You're President Jiang's son.

595
00:38:48,480 --> 00:38:50,720
Xiaomeng, I'm like you.

596
00:38:50,760 --> 00:38:52,000
I just want to be myself.

597
00:38:52,400 --> 00:38:53,360
Upon my coming back,

598
00:38:53,520 --> 00:38:54,840
Internet Plus

599
00:38:55,040 --> 00:38:57,160
and new energy vehicles
have caught my attention.

600
00:38:57,200 --> 00:38:58,200
I want to give it a try.

601
00:38:58,680 --> 00:38:59,800
That's good.

602
00:39:00,000 --> 00:39:01,040
Let's both work hard.

603
00:39:01,320 --> 00:39:02,360
Yep, work hard.

604
00:39:09,280 --> 00:39:10,080
Xiaomeng,

605
00:39:10,120 --> 00:39:11,600
what are you carrying in your bag?

606
00:39:11,640 --> 00:39:12,720
It looks so bulgy.

607
00:39:14,520 --> 00:39:17,280
I bought these boxing gloves for Yan.

608
00:39:17,760 --> 00:39:18,960
Do they look good?

609
00:39:20,840 --> 00:39:23,440
I don't want Yan
to give up the sport he likes.

610
00:39:26,360 --> 00:39:27,640
You bought these for Yan.

611
00:39:30,640 --> 00:39:31,640
I think...

612
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:33,800
the red pair looks better.

613
00:39:52,840 --> 00:39:53,960
Don't let Xiaomeng know that...

614
00:39:54,720 --> 00:39:55,680
I've been to the hospital.

615
00:39:56,280 --> 00:39:57,080
Yes.

616
00:40:04,720 --> 00:40:06,560
The feet can tell
if a pair of shoes suits them.

617
00:40:35,120 --> 00:40:37,200
Jiang Ze, thanks for driving me home.

618
00:40:37,600 --> 00:40:38,960
Feel free to use my car.

619
00:40:39,160 --> 00:40:41,920
Xiaomeng, you don't have to.

620
00:40:42,440 --> 00:40:44,320
If I take your car, how do you go to work?

621
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:46,360
I can call a cab.

622
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:48,600
That's too much trouble.

623
00:40:48,640 --> 00:40:50,200
Where are you going tomorrow?
I'll drive you.

624
00:40:50,760 --> 00:40:51,960
No. You don't have to.

625
00:40:54,240 --> 00:40:55,040
Xiaomeng,...

626
00:40:56,200 --> 00:40:57,360
have you become Miss No?

627
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,160
What do you mean?

628
00:40:59,880 --> 00:41:00,760
Listen to yourself,

629
00:41:00,800 --> 00:41:02,400
how many no's have you said...

630
00:41:02,600 --> 00:41:04,240
since our lunch?

631
00:41:04,840 --> 00:41:06,920
Is "no" the only word you know?

632
00:41:08,640 --> 00:41:09,760
I'm sorry.

633
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,680
You're sorry again.

634
00:41:13,040 --> 00:41:14,200
Could you please...

635
00:41:14,360 --> 00:41:16,480
stop saying "I'm sorry" from now on?

636
00:41:23,280 --> 00:41:24,840
(Pingwang Third Road,
Number 37 Building 5)

637
00:41:29,040 --> 00:41:29,880
Yan!

638
00:41:32,320 --> 00:41:33,280
Jiang Ze, you're here.

639
00:41:33,640 --> 00:41:35,680
Yes. I told you this morning

640
00:41:35,720 --> 00:41:36,800
my car got bumped.

641
00:41:36,960 --> 00:41:38,280
It turned out to be Xiaomeng who did it.

642
00:41:38,520 --> 00:41:40,320
She's lending me her car for two days.

643
00:41:41,360 --> 00:41:42,400
It's really not your day.

644
00:41:45,920 --> 00:41:47,840
Alright. I'll be going home now.

645
00:41:48,160 --> 00:41:49,040
Hold on.

646
00:41:53,440 --> 00:41:54,600
Come in and have a cup of tea.

647
00:41:54,920 --> 00:41:56,320
We can have a good chat.

648
00:41:57,640 --> 00:41:58,720
Forget about the tea.

649
00:41:59,120 --> 00:42:00,560
How about we do some exercise?

650
00:42:01,440 --> 00:42:02,840
It's been a while.

